| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2442 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9804d087-96eb-54e0-9233-7eccd04ac5dd"
